        <div id="main-content">

          <div class="accordion list-group">
            <div class="card">
              <button class="list-group-item" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                <h4> What does Pomodoro mean? <div class="alignright"><ion-icon name="arrow-dropdown"></ion-icon> </div> </h4>
              </button>
              <div id="collapseOne" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p> The Pomodoro Technique uses a timer to break down work into intervals that are generally 25 minutes. This technique helps maximize efficiency in achieving goals within a certain time bound. </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
              <button class="list-group-item" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
