              </button>
              <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p> Our application is designed to be used in three easy steps.
                  1) Authenticating via logging in with Spotify. <br>
                  2) Select the settings you would like for your <b> productivity </b>session. <br>
                  3) Select the settings you would like for your <b> break </b> session. <br>
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
              <button class="list-group-item" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                <h4> What types of playlists can I use? <div class="alignright"><ion-icon name="arrow-dropdown"></ion-icon> </h4>
              </button>
              <div id="collapseThree" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p> At the moment, Pomelody only supports <b> Spotify </b> playlists. We are unable to implement Youtube playlists because of the fact that Youtube does not support background playing and our application's focus is to minimize screen usage.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

